                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-428" type="surname" value="ILLINGWORTH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-428" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE ILLINGWORTH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a plasterer, and live in Stafford-place, Edgeware-road. I was working in Elstree-street on the 28th of Aug.—I left to go to dinner—when I came back these things were all gone—these now produced are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
