                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-429" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD TEBBS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker. These two trowels and a lath hammer were pawned by the prisoner, between two and three o'clock in the day, on the 28th of August.</p>
               <p>
